    <string name="privacy_intro">BCNTransit respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal data. This policy describes what information we collect, how we use it, and what rights you have.</string>
    <string name="privacy_section1_title">1. Information we collect</string>
    <string name="privacy_section1_body">
    • Device identifier (Android ID), used anonymously to improve stability.\n
    • Configuration preferences (dark mode, notifications).\n
    • Aggregated usage data (frequency, errors).\n\n
    BCNTransit does not collect sensitive data, real-time location, or contact information.
</string>
    <string name="privacy_section2_title">2. Use of information</string>
    <string name="privacy_section2_body">
    Data is used exclusively to:\n
    • Display real-time transport information.\n
    • Send incident notifications.\n
    • Improve app performance.
</string>
    <string name="privacy_section3_title">3. Data sharing</string>
    <string name="privacy_section3_body">BCNTransit does not share or sell personal information to third parties. Some technical data may be processed by services like Firebase Cloud Messaging for notifications, under their own policies.</string>

    <string name="privacy_section4_title">4. Security</string>
    <string name="privacy_section4_body">We implement technical and organizational measures to protect your data against unauthorized access, loss, or alteration.</string>

    <string name="privacy_section5_title">5. Your rights</string>
    <string name="privacy_section5_body">You can request the deletion of your local data by uninstalling the application. BCNTransit does not store identifiable data on external servers.</string>

    <string name="privacy_section6_title">6. Changes to this policy</string>
    <string name="privacy_section6_body">This policy may be updated. We will notify you of significant changes via the app or the official website.</string>
